Future goals include:
1. Have a create page and an editing page where you can create, edit, and save your work to your profile.
2. Have your work linked together (ex: character is from this setting from this world in this plot)
3. Make it so that you choose what documents to be public.
4. A friending system to be notified when they post. Also the share functionality to be able to edit one another's work.
5. Image rendering attached to each of your documents.
6. A liking system to be able to determine what are the most popular writings on the website.
